item.title: 508 HELP PLEASE!?! I'm good with Server...1ST 508 Tho
item.dc:creator: @Syfal Syfal
item.description:
@Syfal wrote:

Make sure you run the server before you run the client. Also, make sure you are using a 508 client. You usually get that when you try to use silabsoft/moparscape clients. Try downloading the most updated version of jdk if this doesn’t help. Hope this helps
